headline: Datadog: A Very Vulnerable Rally Ahead Of Q2 Earnings
summary: Datadog trades at a premium despite slowing growth and faces Q2 risks like margin pressure and dilution after its S&P 500 inclusion. Read why DDOG stock is a sell.
